title: talk_michelangelo
position: 300,600
group: michelangelo
color: blue
actor: SENIOR_M
---
<<if not $talked_to_francesco>>
    The spirits of the quarry are not yet ready to speak. #line:0f18cb9 
    Go find Francesco first. #line:096c4a9 
    <<target npc_francesco>>
<<elseif $piece_michelangelo>>
    You already have my piece. Good! #line:0b38a7c 
    Go find the other spirit. #line:0ee14a4 
<<else>>
    <<card ritratto_michelangelo>>
    I am Michelangelo Buonarroti. #line:0d5074d
    Perhaps the greatest sculptor who ever lived. #line:031f19a 
    <<card michelangelo>>
    I came to Carrara in person to choose my blocks. #line:08a0167 
    I spent eight months in these quarries just for the Tomb of Julius II. #line:03053db 
    I trusted no one else to choose the marble for me. #line:0fe51ca 
    <<jump michelangelo_explain_sculpture>>
<<endif>>
===

title: michelangelo_explain_sculpture
position: 450,600
group: michelangelo
color: blue
actor: SENIOR_M
---
Marble is not just a rock. #line:093f019 
It is the most living material in existence. #line:07889b4 
The sculpture is already inside the block. #line:0b42b65 
My work is to remove the excess marble and set it free. #line:02ac4c1 
With this marble I carved the Pieta, the David and the Moses. #line:0466519 
Works that will last for thousands of years. #line:0934417 
<<jump michelangelo_explain_lizzatura>>
===

title: michelangelo_explain_lizzatura
position: 450,700
group: michelangelo
color: blue
actor: SENIOR_M
---
<<card lizzatura>>
But do you know how the marble reached Florence or Rome? #line:07ea82b 
These blocks weigh as much as ten cars. #line:0a400a2 
There were no trucks, no trains. #line:032f1d7 
They used the lizzatura: a wooden sled called a lizza. #line:066b925 
The quarrymen slid it down incredibly steep slopes. #line:0bd0ec9 
They controlled the speed using thick hemp ropes. #line:0a9ebbc 
It was the most dangerous job that existed. #line:0e2fd00 
Many quarrymen lost their lives doing it. #line:093cdd8 
Now I ask you to draw what you have learned. #line:0d4f366 
<<jump michelangelo_activity_intro>>
===

